AWS Budgets allows you set cost and usage of budgets that alerts you when your budget threshold are exceeded or forecast to be exceeded.You can also create budget to track your aggregate Reservation and Saving plans utilization and coverage metric.
STEPS in creating Budget
Sign in to AWS Management console
Navigate and choose Budget
Choose the Budget's type
Then set budget amount
Set Daily, Monthly,Quarterly or annually Budget
I choose Recurrent Budget so it can reset at the end of budget period
Then the period to begin the expiring budget
Then choose the Budget name
I add an alert threshold of 80% of my budget
Then set Email notification preference
Then create Budget.
